headline: Abselion Launches AAVX and AAV9 Total Capsid Quantification Kits
summary: CAMBRIDGE, United Kingdom, September 09, 2025--Abselion launches AAVX and AAV9 Total Capsid Quantification Kits for use with its Amperia™ benchtop quantification platform.
